**Tested URL:** https://www.saucedemo.com/  
**Environment:** Desktop - Chrome / Firefox  

## ðŸ”¹ 1. Login Functionality

| ID   | Title              | Steps                                                                 | Expected Result                                |
|------|--------------------|------------------------------------------------------------------------|------------------------------------------------|
| TC01 | Valid Login        | 1. Open site<br>2. Enter `standard_user` / `secret_sauce`<br>3. Click login | Redirect to product page                        |
| TC02 | Invalid Login      | 1. Enter `invalid_user` / `wrong_pass`<br>2. Click login              | Error message shown                             |
| TC03 | Locked User Login  | 1. Enter `locked_out_user` / `secret_sauce`<br>2. Click login         | Lockout message displayed                       |

## ðŸ”¹ 2. Shopping Cart

| ID   | Title                | Steps                                                        | Expected Result               |
|------|----------------------|---------------------------------------------------------------|-------------------------------|
| TC04 | Add Product to Cart  | 1. Login<br>2. Add product<br>3. Click cart icon             | Product appears in cart       |
| TC05 | Remove from Cart     | 1. Add product<br>2. Go to cart<br>3. Click remove           | Product is removed            |

